  "title": "Operations & Kitchen Crew",
  "description": "<h2><strong>We’re Hiring! Join Our Ayam Bakar Team</strong></h2><p>We are a <strong>modern Indonesian Ayam Bakar food concept</strong> operating in food court retail stalls, serving delicious, quality, and affordable grilled chicken adapted to Singapore tastes.<br />We’re looking for some who love cooking and serving customers to join our growing team.</p><h3><strong>Positions Available</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Service Crew (Part-Time / Full-Time)</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Kitchen Crew (Part-Time / Full-Time)</strong></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Prepare and serve food according to standards</p></li><li><p>Basic food preparation and plating</p></li><li><p>Cashier duties (for service crew)</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of stall</p></li><li><p>Follow food safety and SOP guidelines</p></li><li><p>Work as a team to ensure smooth operations</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>No experience needed (training provided)</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude and willingness to learn</p></li><li><p>Able to work weekends and public holidays (rotational)</p></li><li><p>For kitchen crew: comfortable with hot food and grilling</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Working Hours</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Full-Time:</strong> 5–6 days per week (shift-based)</p></li><li><p><strong>Part-Time:</strong> Flexible shifts available</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Salary & Benefits</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Competitive salary (based on experience)</p></li><li><p>Meals provided</p></li><li><p>Training & career progression opportunities</p></li><li><p>Friendly and supportive work environment</p></li></ul><p>📍 <strong>Work Location:</strong> Food court (Wisma Atria Above Orchard MRT)<br /></p>",
